The paper deals with face recognition and privacy, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and security and privacy (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a framework that involves deep learning models, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper addresses the trade-off between privacy and utility, which is a topic related to social and information networks (cs.SI).
